  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK571">
<l>kaṇṇōṭṭa meṉṉuṅ kaḻiperuṅ kārikai </l>
<l>yuṇmaiyā ṉuṇṭiv vulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world exists through that greatest ornament (of princes), a gracious demeanour.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
